Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.59,1:40:38.80,Revue Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2\blur4}布切れを破いてやる
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.80,1:40:40.97,Revue Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2\blur4}見せてみたい
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.97,1:40:46.40,Revue Song - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2\blur4}くろに染められゆく感情
